Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,## 前奏
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,## 主歌-1
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.86,0:00:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}風雨飄搖，黑暗環繞\NIn the rain or in the dark
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.43,0:00:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我卻總是看得到希望\NI will never lose the spark
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.06,0:00:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就是它帶我度過低潮\Nthat keeps me going when I'm low
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.57,0:00:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}大家都問我如何做到\NEverybody asks me how
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.17,0:00:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}才能撐過這麼多難關\NI get by when I get down
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.77,0:01:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}黑暗沒有那麼可怕\NIt's easy to get through the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.01,0:01:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}只要你知道\Nonce you know
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.38,0:01:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我可以教你怎樣\NI can show you the way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.52,0:01:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}能讓日子過得更明亮\Nto have a brighter day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.89,0:01:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你只要保持微笑\NIt only takes a smile
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.09,0:01:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}做什麼都有意義\Nto make it all worthwhile
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,## 副歌-1
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.47,0:01:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我們能戰勝恐懼，\NWe can conquer our fears,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.17,0:01:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}只要你保持笑容\Nlaugh until happy tears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.44,0:01:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}喜極而泣不難\Nfall to the ground
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.18,0:01:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}如果你害怕擔心，\NIf you're lost and afraid
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.85,0:01:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}覺得樂極就生悲\Nall the good times will fade
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.85,0:01:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就追隨那聲音\Njust follow the sound
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.22,0:01:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}追隨那歡笑聲\NFollow the sound of laughter
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,## 間奏
