Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.41,0:02:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我們能克服一切阻礙\NWe can rise above it all
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.12,0:02:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}只要有朋友們在身旁\Nwith our friends by our side
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.49,0:02:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}用笑臉面對危險\NFace the danger with a grin
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.02,0:02:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}沒有什麼能贏過我們\N'Cause there's no battle we can't win
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.13,0:02:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我們永遠不會輸，永不分開\NWe will never fall, never divide
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.57,0:02:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我們總會找到辦法\NWe will find the way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.50,0:02:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}來面對新的明天\Nto face another day
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.88,0:02:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你只要保持微笑\NIt only takes one smile
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.08,0:02:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}做什麼都有意義\Nto make it all worthwhile
